      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8565995"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/104877425/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u104877425-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/104877425/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">你大姨妈来了</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-27"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-27 18:14:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8565995_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1.	内心，真诚、节制、内敛 2.	绘画是人类独有的行为 3.	精英主义。画画永远是少数人的游戏，少数人在画，少数人在买，大多数人读印刷品而已 4.	画画是游戏，中西方绘画各有其游戏规则，懂得游戏规则才能玩得深入，是为所谓欣赏 5.	文人画注重内心深度，自成境界，但是对于绘画...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8565995_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8565995_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





